parameters: Thief Nora: I can see a big mountain!

Cleric Sophia: Hehe, it seems like we're definitely in the
right place.

Cleric Sophia: The one in front of us is Mount Monimos,
the largest mountain in the empire.

Mage Relm: I had heard about it, but it's really big, isn't
it?
Clea: Let's get a little closer.

Clea: That's Mount Monimos... There's a dragon over
there...

Thief Nora (We finally made it here... If we defeat the
dragon, everyone in the thief guild should be able to find
happiness...)
Thief Nora (I will definitely obtain the dragon's eye...!)

Mage Relm (I'm getting closer to my dream! The time has come
for me to become a true magician recognized by everyone!)

Mage Relm (Even though I should be able to convince them
that I'm an Archmage, if we defeat the dragon, I'll be able
to be with everyone...)

Cleric Sophia (Hehe, I wonder if Eleo-chan would get mad if
I told her that we're actually going to fight a dragon?)

Cleric Sophia (...I can't afford to die for my true purpose,
which is not the dragon extermination.)

Clea (I've been chasing after the dragon ever since I swore
revenge.)

Clea (Meeting with Celis-san, joining the Adventurer's
Guild)

Clea (There have been good things, bad things, and times
when I wanted to cry.)

Clea (My back scar hurts... It reminds me of the bond I had
with my family, torn apart by the dragon's claws.)
Clea (I will settle this and reclaim everything...!)

Clea: ...Let's go back to the Adventurer's Guild and report
that we've found the dragon's whereabouts.
